data.enText: a large, brightly coloured garden flower that is shaped like a ball and made up of many long narrow petals

tr: any of numerous perennial Old World herbs having showy brightly colored flower heads of the genera Chrysanthemum, Argyranthemum, Dendranthema, Tanacetum
the flower of a chrysanthemum plant

value.def: A chrysanthemum is a large garden flower with many long, thin petals.
